# SEO Pre-Completion Checklist

Claude MUST verify ALL Critical items before any page task is marked complete. A page is NOT done until every 🔴 item passes.

## 🔴 Critical — BLOCKS Completion

### Meta & Titles
- [ ] Meta title: 50–60 chars — keyword + "Peterborough" + power modifier
- [ ] Meta description: 140–160 chars — keyword + trust signal + CTA + price/USP — NEVER empty
- [ ] Meta description is UNIQUE — not duplicated on any other page

### Headings
- [ ] Single H1 with primary keyword + "Peterborough" — first heading on page
- [ ] Minimum 3 H2s — each targeting different keyword variation

### Technical Tags
- [ ] `<html lang="en-GB">` set on root layout
- [ ] Canonical tag present — points to production domain (not vercel preview)
- [ ] robots meta: `index, follow` on public pages
- [ ] Open Graph: title, description, image (1200×630), url, locale, siteName — ALL present
- [ ] Twitter Card: card type, title, description, image — ALL present

### Schema
- [ ] JSON-LD schema present in `<head>` — correct type for page
- [ ] Service pages: Service + FAQPage + BreadcrumbList in single @graph block
- [ ] FAQ schema answers match page FAQ content exactly
- [ ] BreadcrumbList on all subpages — correct path and URLs

### Content & Links
- [ ] All images: descriptive alt text — minimum 5 words, keyword-relevant
- [ ] Image filenames: descriptive kebab-case, no typos
- [ ] OG image at `/public/images/og/[slug]-og.jpg` — 1200×630px
- [ ] Internal links: 3+ in body with descriptive anchor text
- [ ] No generic anchors ("click here", "learn more", "this page")

### Phone & NAP
- [ ] NO placeholder phone numbers — `01234 567890` replaced with real number
- [ ] Real phone in `<a href="tel:+44XXXXXXXXXX">` — clickable on mobile
- [ ] WhatsApp link uses real number
- [ ] Phone identical in footer, schema, and GBP

### CTAs
- [ ] Minimum 2 CTAs — hero/top + bottom
- [ ] No placeholder content anywhere (addresses, emails, names, prices)

## 🟡 Important — Fix Same Session

- [ ] Word count meets minimum for page type
- [ ] Trust signals visible: Gas Safe reg, years, star rating
- [ ] Urgency language near CTAs
- [ ] FAQ section with minimum 5 FAQs (service) / 3 FAQs (area)
- [ ] Related services section: 3–4 linked cards
- [ ] Areas section: all 9 areas listed and linked
- [ ] Breadcrumb visible on page

## 🟢 Enhancement — Note for Future

- [ ] Blog content strategy in progress
- [ ] Google Business Profile created and linked
- [ ] Local citations submitted to 10+ directories
- [ ] Review collection active (target 50+ at 4.5★)
- [ ] GA4 analytics + conversion tracking installed
